Solbox ğŸ¶

Solbox is a decentralized music streaming protocol built on the Solana blockchain. It allows artists to mint songs as NFTs, stake for streaming, and earn rewards based on community engagement.

ğŸŒ Vision

Integrating Solbox into the everything app (X), we aim to create an innovative music experience that combines blockchain transparency with community-driven discovery. Through staking, minting, and engagement-based rewards, Solbox redefines music streaming.

âš™ï¸ Tech Stack

Blockchain: Solana (Rust, Anchor)

Frontend: React, Next.js, TailwindCSS

Smart Contracts: Minting, staking, reward systems


ğŸ§  Key Features

NFT-based song publishing

Staking-to-stream model

Reward-sharing pool

Community-driven discovery


